Class AiExpConfig

java.lang.Object
  com.mcc.ul.AiExpConfig

public class AiExpConfig
extends java.lang.Object

This class provides methods to get or set configuration of an analog input subsystem on an expansion device. To create an instance of this class, call the getExpConfig() method of the AiDevice class.
